{"tid":2448561,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"保釋後重返區會 何啟明劉偉聰相擁 劉：咁辛苦出嚟，梗係要開會","createTime":"2021-03-16T04:11:49.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-16T06:16:35.000Z","uid":240362,"like":26,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"344b9cff22351c68218b5b0833ecff0045fcb095","tid":2448561,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T04:11:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/files/styles/w775/public/column_images/03162_0.jpg?itok=Ida38t-V\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Ffiles%2Fstyles%2Fw775%2Fpublic%2Fcolumn_images%2F03162_0.jpg%3Fitok%3DIda38t-V&h=43f21f4f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n（獨媒報導）深水埗區議會今早開會，因參與初選被控串謀嫌顛覆國家政權的何啟明和劉偉聰，獲准保釋外出後重返議會，二人見面相擁。劉偉聰進入會議室後，區議會主席楊彧和袁海文跟他握手。劉偉聰指：「咁辛苦出嚟，梗係要開會啦。」譚國僑回應表示「一定啦」，楊彧則稱「每次都當係最後一次會議。」<br />\n<br />\n劉偉聰：邊個唔掛住我？<br />\n<br />\n在會議開始前，本身是大律師的劉偉聰不減風趣本色，打趣說：「邊個掛住我？邊個唔掛住我？」他又笑說，「佢（何啟明）未返，我哋要齊齊整整開會。」<br />\n<br />\n楊彧主持會議時發言稱，「我哋先感謝劉大狀回歸，何啟明晏啲都會返嚟。」何啟明及後在9時43分進入會議室，向記者說「早晨，早晨」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/51041889662_2740321a80_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flive.staticflickr.com%2F65535%2F51041889662_2740321a80_b.jpg&h=b29b4627&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n議程及後討論「修改深水埗區議會會議常規」，即常規第7條(1)。劉偉聰就修訂補充其法律意見，認為不應賦權予秘書處過大的權力，應改為「秘書須根據主席指示為每一次會議擬定議程」。<br />\n<br />\n民建聯劉佩玉立即表明反對修改，認為應諮詢政府的法律意見，「我哋唔係律師。」劉偉聰立刻舉手稱，「我係！」現場多名議員大笑，有議員稱「民建聯真係忠誠的廢物嚟」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1081440\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1081440&d=HziU8jWK8j2Oa3ZLfTDirGo8q5%2FbnpuKyKF%2Fs7IAglk%3D&h=8f4dbc8c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1081440&h=ff55d4e9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1081440</a>"},{"pid":"7838d1a68d12fe8b0a4d167d3970326bc2c960b9","tid":2448561,"uid":52779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T04:12:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f8e1017a9c94c2f1fa9ade379fadca757424255","tid":2448561,"uid":218731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T04:15:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"628f4459130478959e33ee89a72eae6c3de45222","tid":2448561,"uid":183844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T04:15:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d8aba4a8c9f1d66a0ff245ba60eb6c8fa1160f6","tid":2448561,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T04:16:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"190d132bb648cb98ed118b936d41456f6839877a","tid":2448561,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T04:18:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25861273b8b7c3b871d5c41d894741fec84e9bf0","tid":2448561,"uid":45498,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T04:19:00.000Z","msg":"民建聯劉佩玉立即表明反對修改，認為應諮詢政府的法律意見，「我哋唔係律師。」<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"orange\">劉偉聰立刻舉手稱，「我係！」現場多名議員大笑</span></span>，有議員稱「民建聯真係忠誠的廢物嚟」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b77cd36ac595f40912ef12e27687a6b5dc688d3","tid":2448561,"uid":57674,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T04:22:07.000Z","msg":"忠誠廢物出黎獻世<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" cla